ine\\\" on such incidents happening as a result of posts on their platforms.\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"criticism\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3394}, {\"ngram\": \"social-media bosses\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3422}, {\"ngram\": \"governments\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3447}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"firmer line\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3475}, {\"ngram\": \"such incidents\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3494}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3516}, {\"ngram\": \"posts\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"their platforms\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Sullivan asked an important question when he said to Martin: \\\"Is Elon Musk going to pay any attention to what you say?\\\"\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3601, \"end\": 3607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9999999795359147, \"rank\": 1.564151750584262e-08, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"O'Sullivan\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3556}, {\"ngram\": \"an important question\", \"from\": 3563, \"to\": 3584}, {\"ngram\": \"Elon Musk\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3622}, {\"ngram\": \"any attention\", \"from\": 3636, \"to\": 3649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than insulting Martin, he was pointing out that, for all the fierce words, it might be hard to make an actual impact.\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3691, \"end\": 3697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9999999795359147, \"rank\": 1.564151750584262e-08, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the fierce words\", \"from\": 3729, \"to\": 3749}, {\"ngram\": \"an actual impact\", \"from\": 3776, \"to\": 3792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would think it has to be a European Union approach,\\\" conceded Martin, who went on to call Musk and his site X \\\"problematic\\\".\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3833, \"end\": 3838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999989879143533, \"rank\": 1.0111364331761401e-06, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3859, \"end\": 3865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9999999795359147, \"rank\": 1.564151750584262e-08, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Musk\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3891}, {\"ngram\": \"his site X \\\"problematic\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet onMorning Ireland(RT\\u00c9 Radio 1, weekdays) the next day, Minister for Justice Helen McEntee stopped short of commenting on Musk but would say that social-media platforms \\\"have a lot to answer for\\\".\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 4122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yet onMorning Ireland(RT\\u00c9\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 3948}, {\"ngram\": \"Radio\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 3954}, {\"ngram\": \", weekdays\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 3966}, {\"ngram\": \"Justice\", \"from\": 3995, \"to\": 4002}, {\"ngram\": \"Musk\", \"from\": 4048, \"to\": 4052}, {\"ngram\": \"social-media platforms\", \"from\": 4072, \"to\": 4094}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4101, \"to\": 4106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, by now we already know that.\", \"from\": 4123, \"to\": 4166, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The move towards calling out Musk and X, where far-right members have been able to gather quite the following, is much overdue.\", \"from\": 4167, \"to\": 4294, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The move\", \"from\": 4167, \"to\": 4175}, {\"ngram\": \"Musk\", \"from\": 4196, \"to\": 4200}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 4205, \"to\": 4206}, {\"ngram\": \"far-right members\", \"from\": 4214, \"to\": 4231}, {\"ngram\": \"quite the following\", \"from\": 4257, \"to\": 4276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why do girls as young as seven feel they are held to different beauty standards from boys?\", \"from\": 4296, \"to\": 4386, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4308}, {\"ngram\": \"different beauty standards\", \"from\": 4349, \"to\": 4375}, {\"ngram\": \"boys\", \"from\": 4381, \"to\": 4385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what the psychotherapist and authorStella O'Malleydiscussed with Jonathan Healy (standing in for Ciara Kelly) onNewstalk Breakfast(Newstalk, weekdays) on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 4387, \"to\": 4558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4459, \"end\": 4473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Healy\", \"score\": 0.9999881635512995, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jonathan Healy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Healy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Healy\"}, {\"begin\": 4491, \"end\": 4502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara_Kelly\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ciara Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara_Kelly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ciara_Kelly\"}, {\"begin\": 4525, \"end\": 4533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newstalk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Newstalk\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newstalk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newstalk\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"weekdays\", \"from\": 4535, \"to\": 4543}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 4548, \"to\": 4557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an important conversation; as O'Malley says, a focus on looks can have a negative impact on young girls.\", \"from\": 4559, \"to\": 4668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an important conversation\", \"from\": 4564, \"to\": 4589}, {\"ngram\": \"O'Malley\", \"from\": 4594, \"to\": 4602}, {\"ngram\": \"a focus\", \"from\": 4609, \"to\": 4616}, {\"ngram\": \"looks\", \"from\": 4620, \"to\": 4625}, {\"ngram\": \"a negative impact\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4652}, {\"ngram\": \"young girls\", \"from\": 4656, \"to\": 4667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the analysis was frustratingly narrow at times, particularly around the idea that the issue is largely down to girls being complimented on social media for their looks.\", \"from\": 4669, \"to\": 4841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the analysis\", \"from\": 4673, \"to\": 4685}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 4714, \"to\": 4719}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 4741, \"to\": 4749}, {\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 4755, \"to\": 4764}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 4784, \"to\": 4789}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 4812, \"to\": 4824}, {\"ngram\": \"their looks\", \"from\": 4829, \"to\": 4840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps that's just the nature of having only eight minutes to talk about such a huge topic, but I was itching for a deeper probing of the impact of \\\"vanity\\\" on young girls - and what is even meant by \\\"vanity\\\".\", \"from\": 4843, \"to\": 5053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the nature\", \"from\": 4858, \"to\": 4873}, {\"ngram\": \"only eight minutes\", \"from\": 4884, \"to\": 4902}, {\"ngram\": \"such a huge topic\", \"from\": 4917, \"to\": 4934}, {\"ngram\": \"a deeper probing\", \"from\": 495